Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can keep this all under wraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I want a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some whiskey bon-bons if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I got them from that extraordinary beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk to me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought Inspector Zeman would do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that brings peace to my heart right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,An unbelievable and brutal incident has occurred inside the Prague police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Hamlik, Head Detective Patera, and Detective\NJanacek were poisoned and found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the culprit's purpose in\Ncommitting such a daring crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors talk of a connection between the Czech police\Nand the former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is there a possibility that larger scandals\Nare behind this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Is there a possibility that larger scandals\Nare behind this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is there a possibility that larger scandals\Nare behind this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that the poison used was\Nsome sort of muscle relaxant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that even Chief of Police Hamlik\Nwas connected to the secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a connection to last week's\Nmurder of Inspector Zeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We are still investigating that case, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the investigation department is thinking\Nthat at all the cases are somehow connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, umm, we will consider all possibilities and\Nfrom that we'll continue the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, he is in charge of a different case, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything unnecessary and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When will there be a formal press report?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait until we have all the facts straight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your press report are always too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:26.87,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}\NDouble Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here for data collection again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was ordered by the higher-ups to\Ninvestigate this case from step one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already talked to the other children who were taken in by other nurseries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They saw Mr. Petrov, a man who was like a parent to them, and his female assistant die before their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the children are still having nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to forget about it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, it's not something you can\Never forget even in a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone they loved with their whole hearts was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen minutes per kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask any questions that are too raw for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, living there was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Petrov and Miss Anna were very nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about the day of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever see the man who came to\Nvisit that day, Mr. Grimmer, before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was the first time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were Mr. Petrov and Mr. Grimmer\Ngetting along well together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it didn't seem like they were that close, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They were talking about something serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids know a little German, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "This place doesn't have a license,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and "I'll report you to the police."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He also said something about\N"education" and an "experiment."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are things that you don't want\Nto remember, it's okay, Honza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing was 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a place like that in the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mr. Grimmer... What kind of person was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Izzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He played soccer with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't that good, but he looked like he was having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so bad at heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell on his butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honza's probably the next worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the leader there, weren't you Antonin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a little older than the rest of the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you about that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honza and Izzy said you asked them about Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suspect him do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer isn't the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We were playing soccer with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When we came back, Mr. Petrov and Anna were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We told this to the police before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw a pretty blonde lady leaving our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't decided to do that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised. We even decided on the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? We might arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, he's not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't cry, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He wet the bed twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wet the bed much more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Antonin, do you have what I left you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good job holding onto it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something important that I got from your grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play soccer, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't really have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll play, but just for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It got stolen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta dribble better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Defender!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Mr. Grimmer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go waving a gun around in front of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You throw me your gun first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not carrying a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You tossed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never carried a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who murdered Inspector Zeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tortured and half-dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the one who shot that man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have killed the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team doesn't have enough members now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. I'm completely exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who told them to invite you to play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been betrayed by many people in the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the only one you can trust is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing you can believe in, is you yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me you won't run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you staying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pavla Hotel, Room 302.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can confirm that I'm a criminal,\Ncome whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you hold on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that it's the cause of this series of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the key to his safe deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this signboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sign for a bar from over 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the bar's gone, the sign is still hanging there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The color is fading, but it's a landmark on this street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, many misfortunes\Nmust have befallen this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But this sign survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It even survived the fire some umpteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman with a child moved into the second floor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She was very beautiful, but she seemed pretty gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't come out much and\NI heard she used a fake name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, a black car came out of the blue\Nand took the woman and child away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There were rumors that she was involved\Nwith some anti-government activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the politics of fear back when\Ncommunism was coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a horrible age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't odd for people to just disappear\Noff the face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Were the children she had with her twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there was only one child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the child had such a beautiful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a boy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Now that you mention it, I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're young, you can't really tell sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone said, "I can't believe that they'd take\Na mother, let alone an innocent child away!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that place caught on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire started when you'd think that no one\Nwould be there, but that child was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've released the child alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The child must have been hungry and tried\Nto light a fire in order to make some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That child was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After the child was rescued from the fire,\Nthey lost track of the child's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that child was one of the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What if one of the twins was taken away and the\Nother one was left alone in that apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That is a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you so sure there were twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,About the person you told me to check out, Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help and ended up saying\Nsomething irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was chasing him, I learned many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was eager to avenge the death of Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But while I was conducting the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that Inspector Zeman,\Nwho I respected as a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was in reality, corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, the chief and two\Nof my seniors were poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that they were poisoned,\NI was dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far the world of darkness\Nexpands into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The former secret police of Czechoslovakia are the ones\Npulling the strings behind these recent events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They were an organization under the direct control\Nof the former Ministry of Internal Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the Iron Fist of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago, during the democratic revolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the organization was dissolved and the officers\Nin the organization were put on trial, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,many of them went underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, many of them are plotting to regain\Nthe great power that they once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But why must there be so many sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the secret police the only ones behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much darkness is spreading\Nin the world we live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Grimmer said this to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the end, the only one you can trust is yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When he said that, he gave me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been talking about this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay. You don't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I didn't believe trust could be had
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,between people who didn't know each other's name and personal background.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents were both teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But my dad was singled out by the authorities\Nfor democratic activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom left him for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said I wanted to be a detective, my mom opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to be a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends said it at the bar before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were actually influenced that much by cop dramas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream since I was a kid.\NI've always been a fan of cop dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did he give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You said before that Grimmer gave you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A key to a bank safe-deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A safe deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there's something very important in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has something to do with the case in which the German man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Petrov, was running an unlicensed orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that inside that safe deposit box, there's some\Ndata from human experiments that Mr. Petrov ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be the cause of these series of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk about it to the police or anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this isn't a problem I can handle on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why your mother didn't\Napprove of you being a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought that something might happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She just had a bad feeling about it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you mustn't tell anyone about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the same feeling as your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, what a nice name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're German.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Mr. Trunka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice night, isn't it Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Good Evening, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good everting, Mrs. Jalka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So a safe deposit box key?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:23:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:53.57,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Monster's Afterimage
